<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AROMA Restaurant - Waiter Dashboard</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .header {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            color: #2d3748;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        .nav-tabs {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .nav-tab {
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: #4f46e5;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .nav-tab:hover {
            background: #3730a3;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .nav-tab.active {
            background: #059669;
        }
        
        .stats-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .stat-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            display: block;
        }
        
        .stat-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }
        
        .stat-card.clickable {
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }
        
        .stat-card.clickable:hover {
            border-color: #4f46e5;
        }
        
        .stat-card h3 {
            color: #4f46e5;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .stat-card p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        .welcome-section {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .welcome-section h2 {
            color: #2d3748;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .welcome-section p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .quick-access-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .quick-access-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }
        
        .quick-access-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-color: #4f46e5;
        }
        
        .quick-access-card .icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .quick-access-card h3 {
            color: #2d3748;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .quick-access-card p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .nav-tabs {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
            }
            
            .quick-access-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üçΩÔ∏è AROMA Restaurant - Waiter Dashboard</h1>
            <p>Manage orders, bookings, and customer service</p>
            <div class="nav-tabs">
                <a href="/waiter" class="nav-tab active">Dashboard</a>
                <a href="/waiter/orders" class="nav-tab">üìã Orders</a>
                <a href="/waiter/bookings" class="nav-tab">üìÖ Bookings</a>
                <a href="/waiter/menu" class="nav-tab">üçî Menu</a>
                <a href="/waiter/categories" class="nav-tab">üìë Categories</a>
                <a href="/waiter/qr" class="nav-tab">üî≤ QR Codes</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="stats-grid">
            <a href="/waiter/orders" class="stat-card clickable">
                <h3><%= pendingOrders %></h3>
                <p>Pending Orders</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/waiter/orders" class="stat-card clickable">
                <h3><%= confirmedOrders %></h3>
                <p>Confirmed Orders</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/waiter/bookings" class="stat-card clickable">
                <h3><%= todayReservations %></h3>
                <p>Today's Reservations</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/waiter/menu" class="stat-card clickable">
                <h3><%= menuItems %></h3>
                <p>Menu Items</p>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="welcome-section">
            <h2>üëã Welcome, Waiter!</h2>
            <p>You have access to manage orders, view bookings, check the menu, and generate QR codes for tables.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px;">Use the navigation above or quick access cards below to get started.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="quick-access-grid">
            <a href="/waiter/orders" class="quick-access-card">
                <div class="icon">üìã</div>
                <h3>Manage Orders</h3>
                <p>View and manage customer orders, update statuses, and track payments</p>
            </a>
            
            <a href="/waiter/bookings" class="quick-access-card">
                <div class="icon">üìÖ</div>
                <h3>View Bookings</h3>
                <p>Check today's reservations and upcoming bookings</p>
            </a>
            
            <a href="/waiter/menu" class="quick-access-card">
                <div class="icon">üçî</div>
                <h3>Browse Menu</h3>
                <p>View all menu items, prices, and availability</p>
            </a>
            
            <a href="/waiter/categories" class="quick-access-card">
                <div class="icon">üìë</div>
                <h3>Menu Categories</h3>
                <p>View menu categories and organization</p>
            </a>
            
            <a href="/waiter/qr" class="quick-access-card">
                <div class="icon">üî≤</div>
                <h3>QR Codes</h3>
                <p>Generate QR codes for table ordering</p>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

